---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import promoImage from '../assets/images/vermi.jpg'; 
---

<section id="vermicompostaje" class="py-16 md:py-24 relative z-10">
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md dark:bg-[#291d19]/80 ring-1 ring-black/5 dark:ring-white/10 transition-all duration-500">
      
      <div class="md:w-1/2 relative h-72 md:h-auto group overflow-hidden">
        <Image 
          src={promoImage} 
          alt="Manos con tierra y lombrices"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-white/40 dark:to-[#291d19]/60"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-1/2 relative p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center items-start text-left">
        
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-[var(--color-secondary)] hidden md:block opacity-80"></div>
        
        <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-green-100/80 dark:bg-black/30 text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-6 border border-green-200/50 dark:border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
          CURSO ONLINE
        </span>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Lombricultura <br />
          <span class="text-[var(--color-secondary)]">Humus de Lombriz</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-md font-medium">
          Aprende a transformar tus residuos org√°nicos en el mejor abono para tu tierra. Un ciclo vital que comienza en tu hogar.
        </p>

        <a href="/curso-vermicompostaje" class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-lg font-bold shadow-lg hover:shadow-green-500/30 transition-all group backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span>ACCEDER AL CURSO</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
            </svg>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>